# echarts-cities-js

Inspired by [all-the-cities](https://github.com/zeke/all-the-cities), it brings [cities1000](https://www.npmjs.com/package/cities1000) npm package, which in turn came from [geonames.org](http://download.geonames.org/export/dump/) data.


## 安装 - Installation

```
npm install echarts-cities-js
```

## 版权 - License

All data coordiates are under CC licenses
The code is under MIT

## 维护 - Maintenance

```
pip install moban
npm install
gulp
moban
```
